Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"-1 day before-"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow ended up back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we have to become second-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Down below, Shimamura and our\Nnew classmates are having PE class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Shimamura even realize I'm up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, Shimamura\Nwas surrounded by new people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and things were going well for her,\Nbut not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura was smiling...\Nwith people she barely knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't find a difference in\Nthat smile with the one she showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:01:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It frustrated me, I couldn't breathe,\Nand I felt like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that there was never\Nanything actually dramatic or special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,between Shimamura and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a third-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As she sat a little further down,\Nshe started to read her book quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This calm takes over the area
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I lose my place even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking your spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually knew that Shimamura\Nwould never show up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura and I aren't alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we even met in\Nthe gym was because I'm alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and Shimamura was bored and left class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What I ended up remembering\Nwere precious times with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring. Everything's so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring without Shimamura around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Shimamura would like something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I looking for something\NShimamura might like even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. I think you dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never been interested in stuff like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I had a matching one with Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This was basically a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm the same\Nas that puppy on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I pretty much put myself in that case
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead of being able to attract customers,\NI'm just sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Money, marriage, relationships,\NI'll predict it all!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go home with troubles in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never be able to welcome\Na wonderful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Are you a fortuneteller?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, or perhaps, a fortunegiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you anything you need to know. Even...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...the reason behind those tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be having romance troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Let me just ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that person have longer hair than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that's very dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's hair... is so smooth\Nand pretty... and soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're already lost in thought,\NI think I got the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, what you are lacking...\Nis enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were worried about how\Nothers view you and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very obvious what you're lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you a very simple way\Nyou can gain enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Face that direction and scream.\NRight here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you'll just waste your 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this is what you truly wish for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do I really have to do it\Nright here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, if you don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, scream! Scream everything\Nyou're feeling with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw your arms up and declare it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way you're going to be able\Nto embrace and steel your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is too soft and\Nthat wasn't the best line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't throw up your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking, "If I had the guts to do that,\NI wouldn't have this issue."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this whole issue\Nwould be resolved if you had guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're clearly not. Now, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to have any regrets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you mustn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I can't seem to get over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up just denying how I felt\Nand just ran away from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'd just stopped and\Nactually talked to Shimamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,none of this would've happened.\NA part of me regretted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, excellent. Now, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you actually did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't need to know the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to strongly desire the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thanks, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me.\NMay you have a bright future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the weekend is over, I'll tell Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I told myself and actually came\Nto school, but still, I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"{\i1}Thunderheads and Rain{\i0}\NEiji Kikkawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"{\i1}Thunderheads and Rain{\i0}\NEiji Kikkawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This book...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking your spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"{\i1}Thunderheads and Rain{\i0}\NEiji Kikkawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why did I keep running? Because I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I spend every day afraid thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,what if my tomorrow becomes\Nyesterday to the rest of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as I waste time hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be left behind because of\Nsome great change I don't know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather run to the front and choose a path\Nwhere I can make the change myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Shimamura was able\Nto become a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura is in class right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's eating lunch. She's not coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason she would.\NOkay, I've got to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in a club is sort of a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--There's no room\Nin the place I want to go.\N--They're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--But...\N--Relationships are so hard.\N--You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--Relationships are so hard.\N--You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--Then I'll just have to make room.\N--By the way, on our way home,\Nwanna get pancakes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Shi--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was my official start\Nas a second-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it'd been\Nsince I heard Adachi's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this was the first time\Nin this classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, let me get you a seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shimamura. I bought some breads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This many? Isn't this a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have whichever one you want, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have the jam bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I can't eat that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a little embarrassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think she made up her mind\Nthat I'm the only one she needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about me, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times if I even really need anyone,\Nand I still don't have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did know was my flimsy relationship\Nwith Sancho and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,would fade away even before\Nwe changed seats again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just teasing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these popular right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was thinking of getting one, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd be matching...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Adachi got one, she'd be\Nmatching with me and Tarumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone want to\Nhold my hand so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they all think I'm going\Nto wander off somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NTarumi takes my left hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but Adachi takes my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Adachi. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your bike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see each other tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't actually go home\Nunless you let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're not going anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere. Nope, nope, nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... She reminds me of a sad little puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think you're the best, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, where did this... uh, hug come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We hadn't done anything in a while, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Done anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were with those other girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Adachi not only want me\Nto be her big sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but also her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sancho and the others saw us right now,\Nthey'd really get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've gotta get home, little Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you treating me like a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can I call you later?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me? Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you... around seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I eat dinner around seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, if it isn't Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some strawberry shortcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But where did you guys get money for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think Yachi pulled this cake\Nout of her pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to become Yashiemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yashiemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you'd like,\NShimamura, just--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home. Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have dinner earlier? I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making dinner right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like some sweet crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where did you get those?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am Yashiemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to eat earlier\Nthan everyone else then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. What's for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakitori I just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you chopping it up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Adachi, she'll probably\Ncall me right at seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's sitting very rigidly\Nin front of her phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"4/21 (Tue)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Adachi\NIncoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we go. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening. Are your legs asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a guess. So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you wanted to talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hadn't called you for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to make any friends, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"And"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have you, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Adachi always talk like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you talk to anyone else\Non the phone, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you sound so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I thought I was the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one that I call, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to just end the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're not going to talk,\Nit's sort of a waste of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all! I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm on the phone with you,\NI get to have your time all to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bit possessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I-I think it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is totally normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end, it's not a bad feeling\Nknowing that someone cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Adachi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shimamura\NIn Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shimamura\NIn Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Himamuwa... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with Adachi,\Nmy possibilities are fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to choose someone\Nto walk alongside with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The choices get narrowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I should choose whatever's best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that Adachi has chosen the path\Nwhere she doesn't need anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 11: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 11: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Friends and Love,\NLove and Cherry Blossoms'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Friends and Love,\NLove and Cherry Blossoms'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: The final episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Friends and Love,\NLove and Cherry Blossoms'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--I've realized something insane.\N--What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If we never air the next episode,\Nthe final episode will never come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning this anime will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure people will just think\Nit got canceled then.
